div.head:
Certain Observations, Collected out of a Treatise, called, The difference between Christian Subjection, and unchristian Rebellion;
                  Allowed by publike Anthority to be set forth, as in the title page may appear.
                Compiled by that judicious and learned Divine, Tho: Bilson, then Warden of Winchester, since Bishop there; necessary in these times to be perused.
